casebody.data:
No. 65,

Orig.

Texas v. New Mexico. [For earlier order herein, see, e, g., 495 U. S. 901.]

Final Report of the River Master for Accounting Year 1990 adopted. Motion of the River Master for approval of fees and expenses granted, and the River Master is awarded $5,063.44 for the period April 1 through June 30, 1990, to be paid equally by the parties.
